            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/01/rgg-like-a-dragon-direct-set-for-january-9-featuring-deeper-dive-into-like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Including first looks at Majima in Ichiban Kasuga's outfits.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,641 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio [483 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega/ryu-ga-gotoku-studio">Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio</a> will host an “RGG <em>Like a Dragon</em> Direct” on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250109T1700" rel="noopener" target="_blank">January 9 at 9:00 a.m. PT / 12:00 p.m. ET</a>, the companies announced. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=viAEO_cMqfU" rel="noopener" target="_blank">YouTube</a>. <span id="more-937142"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature a deeper dive into <em><a title="Games > Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii">Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</a></em>, including various updates and first looks at new features, like how Goro Majima can change into two of Ichian Kasuga’s iconic outfits.</p><p><em>Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,624 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,542 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,569 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,691 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [22,072 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3061810/Like_a_Dragon_Pirate_Yakuza_in_Hawaii/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii/9p1303fcxw6x" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on February 21 worldwide.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
